project_descr: Ministry of Public Commission for the Protection of Marine Resources, Environment & Wild life -  Phase-out of Ozone Depleting Substance of CFCs (TPMP)

outputs.output_descr: The Terminal Phase-Out Management Plan, jointly implemented by UNDP and UNEP, will result in the complete phase-out of Chlorofluorocarbons (CFCs) in the Kingdom of Bahrain.

project_title: phase-out of ozone depleting substance of cfcs (tpmp)
